{"type": "article", "id": 12446, "title": "Paul Gaultier 为茶叶设计新包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-22T07:45:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071042342ciHOIXewkTbvuzN.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t近日，Jean-Paul Gaultier 与 Kusmi Tea 合作，为后者品牌中两个最受欢迎的口味 “Anastasia” 和“Prince Wladimir” 重新设计了外包装。这些茶叶有着一些传统和古老的故事，据说是受到了圣彼得堡诺曼诺夫王朝沙皇尼古拉二世的女儿 Anastasia ，以及俄罗斯弗拉基米尔的故事的影响。于是 Jean-Paul Gaultier 在设计中主要展现二十世纪八十年代，加入其经典的水手条纹与刺青花纹，刚柔结合。除了茶叶盒子，此次推出的还有一个刺青马克杯，带有一个可以拆卸的过滤网。这是<a href=\"http://en.kusmitea.com/kusmiandjeanpaulgaultier\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140204MAn0Sc9sNmvKr3ea.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140204RFXLjT1Bcw2uKD3C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66796875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140205PgeQ5HLKzoxXOmt8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66796875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140205SQtWn6m1YKFsgoIe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140206oNmbiOzCEHwg6LqB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.03300733\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140206PkZxGjAL7R0cebmn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66595745\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}